Updates to Linux

All functions work on Linux now (mtGenome_Assembly_Nick.R)

interleave paired read files using BBMap

Parallel Version Fix

Fixed bug in the parallel version of mtGenome_Assembly.R. The 'writeLines' function has funny behavior in a loop, so I switched to 'write' instead.
added mitoChop and align to reference

Added MAFFT

MUSCLE was conking out on the Varanus assemblies for some reason, so I've added MAFFT as an alternate aligner
